{
  "stem": "3804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was like a-- you know, more than a mother to me than a sister because we had-- there was a big difference in years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was very occupied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was all the time going abroad to bring this wheat and all this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With my brother, how you say, been a very good relationship because he was not only my brother, also my friend.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like if we have to go to swim, we go together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To the forest, we go together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have also been small groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had one friend of mine, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was kind of a small sculpture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we played mostly in the graveyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You ask me why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The graveyard was the most silent place, and they had a big space.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think most-- many Jewish children played in the graveyard because that was the only place that they wouldn't have goyim.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They wouldn't have Polish there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And also you have space.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you have hiding places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I liked it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Even people hate, you know, and they're afraid of graveyard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I still have the atmosphere when I come to a graveyard, the most important thing is how the trees are, how the wind comes, and if it's not too crowded.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I already said to somebody, if you want to put me somewhere after my death, put me in a small place, not in the city because even the graves out there are crowded like crazy.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Put me in the place that somebody can read my name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it shouldn't be fancy and all this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A small place.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's exactly what was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I visit later this graveyard in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
